{"tid":370644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當本港風勢進一步減弱　天文台將改發三號信號","createTime":"2017-08-23T06:48:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T05:53:57.000Z","uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4f7e2ca6f5b21cf4ff8f6e15f81546abb64095bb","tid":370644,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:48:22.000Z","msg":"八號東南烈風或暴風信號生效，天文台說，隨著強颱風天鴿逐漸遠離，本港風力正在減弱，當本港風勢進一步減弱，不再受烈風或暴風影響，天文台會改發三號強風信號。<br />\n<br />\n在下午2時，天鴿集結在香港以西約110公里，預料向西北偏西移動，時速約25公里，移入廣東內陸並逐漸減弱。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1349887-20170823.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1349887-20170823.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=nO9b1a1YD2by4zN8IxcPMp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=c1244f1d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1349887-20170823.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a49b4f1c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1349887-20170823.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"14c7def729f26ed821836dde3b135bbcefd7a452","tid":370644,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:51:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7286d73d98890c6aeaa7ee1e41e77691357c7a70","tid":370644,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:54:08.000Z","msg":"頂到4點呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324586bc7a6e45a641f3fa7535e04e0040229bb4","tid":370644,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:55:31.000Z","msg":"番工撚準備全面進場"},{"pid":"4056afe427e236e83afae9199ed9785be0fb0578","tid":370644,"uid":40644,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:55:51.000Z","msg":"快d 落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif